Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! This boy here is awfully late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a good Homer nods sometimes. {even monkeys fall from trees; anyone can make a mistake; pride comes before a fall; even Homer sometimes nods}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even experts make mistakes! {Homer sometimes nods; even Kōbō Daishi's handwriting contains mistakes​}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Buddha can misread the sutra! {釈迦にも経の読み違い}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a kappa can drown in the river! {anyone can make a mistake; even Homer sometimes nods​}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch it, you clutz! \NLook where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry. Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it's just Ijigawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What difference does it make?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.96,0:05:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you who bumped into me \Nbecause you were walking and reading!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:02.92,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5FB5AF&\bord1}Playful Comic {おちゃめコミック}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you walking \Nwith your eyes on the book yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ijigawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're standing on a dog poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pathetic, Ijigawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stepped in poop! In poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, it stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It stinks so much even my eyes are stinging! {tlc, I hear **made shibite kuruze - my ** goes numb} {5:28: I'm hearing 目まで染みてくるぜ\NLit: Even my eyes are stinging. - Au}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rich of you, \Nwearing poop on your head yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is a bogus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go tell everyone at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait I said, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijigawa the Stinker! {(you're) dirty!; (you have) cooties!​}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stinker! Stinker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't bumped into Ijigawa, \NI'd have stepped in poop myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:05:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We in school! Yeah! {tlc, you hear anything?}{5:58: I do but I can't make it out.}{a complete guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What happened, Korekiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I... Ah. Doesn't matter{/piss off/shut up}. Hurry up inside. {hope he means this, not in manga; assumed he was made to stand outside for coming late}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Oaya-sensei had to go on a business trip, \Nso I'm conducting the homeroom in her stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyodo-sensei! I'm so sorry for coming late... {name not in manga, unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, that was commendable of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A police officer called us earlier. He said you had to stop by \Nto return lost money, therefore you'd be late. {/despite being late ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud to know we have exemplary students \Nlike you right here in our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, everyone, a round of applause for Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Attaway, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I came late, but instead of slapping, I got an applause! {/I came late, but I got an applause instead of a punishment!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I'm so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it just me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Taru, isn't there some item even more powerful \Nthan Small Forturd for increasing my luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! A whole caboodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Medium Forturd. Wearing this \Nboosts luck even more than Small Forturd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get even luckier than before? \NCan't wait to see it in action!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan in her underwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange... Gym class \Nwas supposed to be during the 5th period.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Because Oaya-sensei is absent, \Nthe timetable was altered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Insanely lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, though it may seem a little sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,for the next class, we'll hold a mini-test in math.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)\c&HA58BC6&\3c&H68852A&}Eek! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? A test? {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:06.15,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,200)\c&HB7BFBF&\3c&H788475&} Test
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even wearing Medium Forturd doesn't help...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can glance at Harako's answers! Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to copy them all! 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this, Jabao? \NAin't that impressive? What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Piss off. Doncha get your nose in the air \Njust 'cause you racked up a good score once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only saying that 'cause you're fuming with jealousy! {Only saying that 'cause you've scored squat!} {guess, kinda hear torenaimondakara, ***; TLC}{10:09: I'm hearing 取り柄もんだからやっかんであがんのよ\NI'm not sure this is very accurate though.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get this! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This ain't half-bad! Lucky, lucky! \NGreatly lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, Taru! You got any other guys \Nin the Forturd Series?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! A whole caboodle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is for oppositing your fate, Oppoositer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This - for increased earnings, Fundung.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This - helps you win lotteries, Drawpping. {I ran out of poop puns several months ago}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That one brings bad luck, Catastrofeces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And... This for happy love, Romanure... {恋愛}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And this... This...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember all the kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, how about we try them on \Nto remember better, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to study more! \NUsing things you don't understand is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you be such a bore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:11:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... What... happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The room is covered in poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Hide them all now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll do right now... {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This, and this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll keep this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? What was {\i1}what{\i0}, mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, let's go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Me sleepy. Come later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I try it out? \NSomething this big surely makes one insanely lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of holding up an umbrella, \Nhe put poop on his head?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a local yokel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, what the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dripping wet... \NYou didn't bring an umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But it started raining out of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see the weather forecast on TV, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They issued a warning for heavy rain \Nthat was starting as soon as this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I... {could be anything}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps a dunce such as you can't even understand \Nwhat the weather forecast says?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's be on our way, Iyona-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best that you don't associate with such miserable men, \Nwearing poop on their heads. Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the latest fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,DON'T TOUCH.{unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get any closer, \Nyou'll get Iyona-san's beautiful clothes all wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's not linger, Iyona-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shithead, literally!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H193704&} Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Edojo Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to the staff room later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like a few words with you \Nregarding yesterday's mini-test.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone notice me cheating? {/cheating/cunning (lol)}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, did you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheated on it, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I also found it was strange that an idiot \Nsuch as Honmaru would get the same score as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very low, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ijigawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun is a brute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He pushed me yesterday on purpose \Nand made me step on dog poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You did that on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell no! You caused that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, yesterday, Honmaru-kun \Nlooked into the class while the girls were changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wasn't trying...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Honmaru is a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fighting him with my bare hands, \Nbut he used a stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Honmaru buying a manga magazine \Neven though he was terribly late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a devil, Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's the deal with that stupid hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun, it seems you'll have plenty \Nto answer for in the staff room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell...? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My luck is ridiculously bad today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious! Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:17:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Why didn't you come to school? \NAll hell broke loose today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That... The Great Shitaclism, \Nsummoning only the worst disasters upon the wearer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:27.58,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,200)\c&H090814&\3c&H8F747F&\t(1100,1100,\3c&H73C6D3&)} The Great Shitaclism {大運凶}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is serious, Taru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll have to repay \Nthe luck Forturd-kun gave him all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't take it off soon, \NHonmaru-kun might even die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! I can't take it off! It won't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So this thing is responsible \Nfor all of my misfortunes today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch-ouch-ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama-chan, is there some good way to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know as soon as I find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, try your best to take it off fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Honmaru! Gotta take Forturd-kun off! Now! {guess, tlc, don't hear a single thing; not in manga either}{18:08: I'm hearing よし、本丸、おいていくぞう but I'm not 100% sure tbh.\NI think what you have now is fine. }
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it off... What... What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{⊗樺島建設 ◇安全为一}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What is this? What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, hurry up! Hurry and take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use! It won't budge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, please use \Nwhatever magic you have to take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I keep attracting nothing but disasters, \Nno amount of lives would be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Control lost! I repeat! Control lost! {不能} {no clue what's this machi bit in the middle}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A plane this time? It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is my life coming to an end now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All because I put this item on my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Control regained!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Oppoositer Mk-3!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand how, but I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Ria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was dangerous, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lucky I put Oppoositer Minus Mk-3 on your head \Nand reversed the power of your previous poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru is also quite a dum-dum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You could just make Honmaru smaller \Nto take it off at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Trunsform.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing called "luck" \Nis something you carve out on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you rely on magic, you'll have to pay the price someday. {ill effects; negative consequences; burden; strain; brunt; loss​}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You should only shape your fate with your own efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,By doing good things for those around you, \Nyou'll have good things coming back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And doing bad things \Nwill bring back things in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Ria said the same thing \Nmom told me back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, remember. If you're kind to people, \Nyou'll only ever get happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it really is the whole gist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I was way unluckier today \Nthan I was supposed to be! {no clue what he means, not in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Poke-poke. {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He put out another one \Nfrom the Forturd Series to play with?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:22:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Wait a moment. \NWhat if it's another one of the Shitaclism kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there. There-there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just some small one Taru wants to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be harmless! {/it probably isn't weird}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have this, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, that's real dog poop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of the Great Shitaclism power rubbed off on you! {/remained}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the worst day ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.39,0:22:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stinker, stinker!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, this wretch Ijigawa is getting too comfortable! {no clue what's this last attama ni kita bit}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Making fun of me getting bad test scores!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taruruuto, isn't there something \Nthat'd help me show her her place? {being argued into silence; being left speechless - unsure what's this about}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.38,0:22:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna hear you show her her place!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:22:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta do something, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, try this...
